<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="習禪" xml:id="gsz0758b22shiZhiWei"><lb
ed="T" n="0758b22"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0758b22"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000008805">金陵天保寺</placeName><ptr target="#n1359"/><persName key="A010051">智威</persName>傳（<persName key="A010075">本淨</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0758b23"/><persName key="A010051">釋智威</persName>，俗姓陳氏，<placeName key="PL000000008820">江寧</placeName>人也。住近<placeName key="PL000000009132">青山</placeName>，地<lb
ed="T" n="0758b24"/>盤嘉氣，善符宿瑞，維嶽降神<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1394"/>。爰在童年，器<lb
ed="T" n="0758b25"/>殊眾識，至於戲弄，曾不染俗。性惡浮飾，<lb
ed="T" n="0758b26"/>人皆異焉。無何一朝，忽失其所，父母莫知<lb
ed="T" n="0758b27"/>攸往，乃遍歷諸寺尋訪之，<persName key="A010051">威</persName>已依<placeName key="PL000000009069">天保寺</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0758b28"/><persName key="A010141">統<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>。誦大乘經，早數百紙，聰敏超倫，眾咸<lb
ed="T" n="0758b29"/>歎服。<date key="j19665031966868" from-iso="+0672-01-01" to-iso="+0672-12-31">年二十</date>，遇恩剃落，隷名于<placeName key="PL000000009186">幽巖寺</placeName>，因<pb ed="T" n="0758c" xml:id="T50.2061.0758c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0758c01"/>從<persName key="A010050">持<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>諮請禪法，妙達深理，繼踵前修。<lb
ed="T" n="0758c02"/>既獲髻珠<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1395"/>，淡然閑放，形容溫潤，面如滿月，<lb
ed="T" n="0758c03"/>言辭清雅，慧德蘭芳。望重一期<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1179"/>，聲聞遠近，<lb
ed="T" n="0758c04"/><placeName key="PL000000000197">江左</placeName>定學往往造焉。其中頓悟心源，即<persName key="A010048">慧<lb
ed="T" n="0758c05"/><anchor xml:id="beg0758003"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>思</sic><corr>忠</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0758003"/>禪師</persName><ptr target="#n1361"/>，乃命嗣山門，盛傳道化。<persName key="A010051">威</persName>自出<lb
ed="T" n="0758c06"/>止<placeName key="PL000000008805">延祚寺</placeName>，說法利人，廣施饒益。以<date key="j19848361984836" when-iso="+0722-03-13">開元十年<lb
ed="T" n
="0758c07"/>二月十八日</date>，終于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000008805">住寺</ref>，遺囑林中飼鳥獸，<lb
ed="T" n="0758c08"/>弟子<persName key="A010143">玄挺</persName>等依言奉行。春秋七十七。<persName key="A010051">威</persName>一時<lb
ed="T" n="0758c09"/>夜行頭陀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g357"/>，將值天曉，有三虎遇之。<persName key="A010051">威</persName>截<lb
ed="T" n="0758c10"/>路中過，了無怖色。虎隨至山門，四顧而去。<lb
ed="T" n="0758c11"/>每有二兔一犬庭際遊戲，各無間畏。蓋大悲<lb
ed="T" n="0758c12"/>平等，物我一均，故其然也。次<placeName key="PL000000028773">司空山</placeName><persName key="A010075">釋本淨</persName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0758c13"/>姓張氏，<placeName key="PL000000021676">東平</placeName>人也<ptr target="#n1362"/>。少入空門，高其節操。遊<lb
ed="T" n="0758c14"/>方見<ref type="person" target="#A001719">曹溪六祖</ref>，決了疑滯。<date notBefore-iso="+0713-12-26" key="j19818371984406" notAfter-iso="+0721-01-07">開元初</date>於<placeName key="PL000000028773">南嶽<lb
ed="T" n="0758c15"/>司空山</placeName>閑放自處，人不我知<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1396"/>，蔽偽之故也。<lb
ed="T" n="0758c16"/><date notBefore-iso="+0742-02-14" key="j19921141997410" notAfter-iso="+0756-08-15"><name>天寶</name>中</date>因<persName key="A010150">楊庭光</persName>采藥，邂逅相逢，論道終<lb
ed="T" n="0758c17"/>日，迴奏，詔赴<placeName key="PL000000042189">京</placeName>，於<placeName key="PL000000042285">白蓮華亭</placeName>安置<ptr target="#n1363"/>。<ref type="person" target="#A000291">帝</ref>知佛<lb
ed="T" n="0758c18"/>法幽深，孰堪商攉<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1397"/>，勅召<placeName key="PL000000023592">太平寺</placeName><persName key="A010148">遠<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>及兩<lb
ed="T" n="0758c19"/>街三學<ptr type="glossary" target="#g182"/>碩德，發問鋒起，若百矢之逐一兔<lb
ed="T" n="0758c20"/>焉。<persName key="A010075">淨</persName>舉措容與，四面枝梧<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1398"/>，譬<persName key="A006931">墨翟</persName>之解九攻<lb
ed="T" n="0758c21"/>機械矣<ptr target="#n1364"/>。既而辯若建瓴<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1399"/>，詶抗之餘，乃引<lb
ed="T" n="0758c22"/>了義教援證。復說「伽陀」<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1400"/>，一無留滯。皇情懌<lb
ed="T" n="0758c23"/>悅，觀者歎嗟<ptr target="#n1365"/>。以<date key="j19991761999176" when-iso="+0761-06-16">上元二年五月五日</date>歸寂<ptr target="#n1366"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0758c24"/>壽齡九十五。勅諡<persName key="A010075">大曉禪師</persName>，亦帶所居為<lb
ed="T" n="0758c25"/>名，曰<persName key="A010075">司空山禪師</persName>也。</p>
